	Types: Pokemon, @C*

	hasLvl @D* (xsd:integer mm:capturing("([0-9]+)")),
	hasMoveSlot1 @E* (rdfs:label),
	hasMoveSlot2 @F* (rdfs:label),
	hasMoveSlot3 @G* (rdfs:label mm:ProcessIfEmptyLocation),
	hasMoveSlot4 @H* (rdfs:label mm:ProcessIfEmptyLocation)
